org.matsim.facilities

Class MatsimFacilitiesReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.matsim.core.utils.io.MatsimXmlParser
        • org.matsim.facilities.MatsimFacilitiesReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatsimReader, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler

    public class MatsimFacilitiesReader
extends MatsimXmlParser
    A reader for facilities-files of MATSim. This reader recognizes the format of the facilities-file and uses the correct reader for the specific facilities-version, without manual setting.
    Author:
    mrieser
